    • Method Detail

      • createSettings

        public static de.braintags.io.vertx.pojomapper.init.DataStoreSettings createSettings()
        This method creates new datastore settings for mongo by using system properties
        • "connection_string" to set the connection of the database
        • "startMongoLocal" wether to start mongo temporary local or expecting a running instance
        • "localPort" If START_MONGO_LOCAL_PROP is set to true, then this defines the local port to be used. Default is 27017
        • defaultKeyGenerator to set the name of the default keygenerator to be used
        Returns:
